durl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404043310/http://www.seph.sh.cn/books/bkview.asp?bkid=4214&cid=7465 |archivedate=2017-04-04}}</ref>[[上海教育出版社|上海教育出版社]]、<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.shkpzx.com/9316/9317/9348/10474.html |title=「發現之旅」叢書 |website=shkpzx.com |language=zh-CN |accessdate=2017-04-03 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112230122/http://www.shkpzx.com/9316/9317/9348/10474.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[上海人民出版社|上海人民出版社]]陸續推出。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://book.douban.com/subject/1863800/ |title=凱爾特人的歐洲 |website=book.douban.com |language=zh-CN |accessdate=2017-04-17 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112230140/https://book.douban.com/subject/1863800/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>一般情況下，時報版與簡體中文版在序號、譯名和譯者方面基本相同，但也有較多差異。例如，時報版由陳太乙翻譯的第65冊《馬諦-{}-斯：揮灑絢麗色彩》，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=mcec(SellItems)&id=XB0065 |title=馬諦斯(XB0065)──揮灑絢麗色彩 |website=readingtimes.com.tw |language=zh-TW |accessdate=2017-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112230135/http://www.readingtimes.com.tw/ReadingTimes/ProductPage.aspx?gp=productdetail&cid=mcec%28SellItems%29&id=XB0065 |dead-url=no }}</ref>簡體版為第66冊，由沈志紅翻譯，譯名《馬蒂斯：傑出的色彩大師》。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://book.douban.com/subject/1737087/ |title=馬蒂斯：傑出的色彩大師 |website=book.douban.com |language=zh-CN |accessdate=2017-04-05 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112230141/https://book.douban.com/subject/1737087/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，簡體版因分別由多家出版社推出，造成少數序號重複或無序號的情況出現。由於時報文化自2006年以後便不再發行這套叢書，而中國大陸則一直陸續出版、再版至近幾年，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jlpg.cn/2015/6/product/1ce5c97dc5b4.HTML |title=2015年再版的《達·芬奇：宇宙的藝術和科學》 |website=jlpg.cn |language=zh-CN |accessdate=2017-06-09 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112230200/http://www.jlpg.cn/2015/6/product/1ce5c97dc5b4.HTML |dead-url=no }}</ref>